      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――雑誌企画『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "インタビュー中",
      "startTime": 2.0533332269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ありがたいことに\n誕生日当日はお仕事が入っています",
      "startTime": 6.2999996263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "プレゼントにほしいもの……？\nそうですね……しいて挙げるとすれば――",
      "startTime": 12.1999998171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――インタビュー後のレッスンスタジオ",
      "startTime": 17.0333337227,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.6653075999982,
          "startTime": 18.8999990303
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。お疲れ、莉央\n意外と終わるの早かったね",
      "startTime": 22.7333329359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "葵こそ、随分と余裕そうじゃない\n今日の練習はもう終わったのかしら？",
      "startTime": 28.715895756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "とっくに終わったよ。今は休憩中なんだ\nこれを読んでたところ",
      "startTime": 35.0333334445,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4447.483150199996,
          "startTime": 35.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、過去の\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の記事ね",
      "startTime": 38.4839657861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "『アイドルの願いごとを叶える誕生日企画』だって\n芽衣も渚も好き放題やらせてもらったみたいだよ",
      "startTime": 45.8666624545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、さっきそれのインタビューを受けてたんだよね\n何をお願いしたの？",
      "startTime": 53.3333291212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに特別なことは言ってないわ",
      "startTime": 55.0240993897,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}